          "name": "HetroSync",
          "description": "",
          "date": "April 2025",
          "summary": "<ul><li><p>Engineered a data synchronization system across heterogeneous databases by implementing custom GET, SET, and MERGE operations with structured operation logs, enabling reliable state convergence.</p></li><li><p>Designed and developed an abstract merge method to synchronize system states using oplogs, ensuring consistency without direct cross-system access, and incorporated mathematical properties like associativity and idempotency.</p></li><li><p>Developed dual execution modes - an interactive CLI for real-time user commands and a test case mode for batch processing via input files using a robust command parser to simulate and validate synchronization and merge operations across systems.</p></li></ul>",
